{"tid":248332,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"為食女立志做醫生","createTime":"2017-05-18T12:56:18.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-18T15:04:25.000Z","uid":40628,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6ceb54ec5d94e30be05ba75b021d40cedc070c4b","tid":248332,"uid":40628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T12:56:18.000Z","msg":"環姐冠軍被爆與最靚仔醫生拍拖<br />\n2016年03月21日(一) 06:50<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20160321/photo/bkn-20160321065054321-0321_00862_001_05b.jpg?20160321085937\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20160321%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20160321065054321-0321_00862_001_05b.jpg%3F20160321085937&h=3d6d8e9c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n俊男美女真係幾配！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【<a href=\"http://on.cc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fon.cc&d=sJi30nZJaTuGAzS5CtepdDOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=8adcdb3f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">on.cc</a>東網專訊】 早前環球小姐競選發生咗單超爆嘅新聞，宣布冠、亞軍時竟然搞錯咗，原本亞軍嘅哥倫比亞小姐阿里阿德娜（Ariadna Gutierrez）變咗冠軍，個后冠都未戴夠一分鐘就畀人除番落嚟，「失而復得」嘅菲律賓小姐皮婭（Pia Alonzo Wurtzbach）就成為最後大贏家。<br />\n皮婭因為呢件事注目度畀歷屆環姐冠軍都要高，好多人都關心佢嘅感情問題，皮婭就話為咗履行環姐嘅職務，其他嘢都會放低先，點知話口都未完，就有傳皮婭同被喻為最靚仔嘅醫生Mikhail Varshavski拍拖，靚仔醫生嘅追隨者即時心都碎埋，不過睇番佢哋自己甫嘅合照，俊男美女，又真係幾襯喎！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20160321/photo/bkn-20160321065054321-0321_00862_001_02b.jpg?20160321085937\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20160321%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20160321065054321-0321_00862_001_02b.jpg%3F20160321085937&h=0c75b9eb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n合照合照<br />\n被喻為最靚仔嘅醫生Mikhail Varshavski。被喻為最靚仔嘅醫生Mikhail Varshavski。<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20160321/photo/bkn-20160321065054321-0321_00862_001_03b.jpg?20160321085937\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20160321%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20160321065054321-0321_00862_001_03b.jpg%3F20160321085937&h=8d50dccc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n合照合照<br />\n呢一幕夠晒經典。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20160321/photo/bkn-20160321065054321-0321_00862_001_04b.jpg?20160321085937\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20160321%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20160321065054321-0321_00862_001_04b.jpg%3F20160321085937&h=bc48ebbb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n環姐冠軍皮婭（Pia Alonzo Wurtzbach）"},{"pid":"cd6f4ce28382607192ae0b5c2ce1e7e2b866628a","tid":248332,"uid":40628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T13:02:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a98dcc90a7e523851490521b718b6a984ddc078","tid":248332,"uid":83388,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T13:04:32.000Z","msg":"好撚柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />個環姐 好撚似拍hardcore av果d 鬼妹"},{"pid":"b11e091a3d149aba312c56f3f23ad7043926e7ac","tid":248332,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T13:17:38.000Z","msg":"好型仔"},{"pid":"68ba5ea036c339e4b4117056f198d6f28fe414d4","tid":248332,"uid":40628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T13:23:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好撚柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />個環姐 好撚似拍hardcore av果d 鬼妹</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有無link <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0efe4bfd226ba86c0654cc74c707b7765607cd8c","tid":248332,"uid":17558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T13:52:49.000Z","msg":"為食女 立志做醫生"},{"pid":"137ee2786ee6be5a56ba3558152f33e2b092c24c","tid":248332,"uid":51129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T13:54:54.000Z","msg":"又回帶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b5c85dba9f826f8052aa496857bcad6743